MHill (08-Dec-97):

There are two ways of configuring "Post In Location" and "Post Out Location".

Using !Connect Configure/Directories gives a basic dialogue box with "Cancel"
and "OK" buttons.

Using !Mail Mail/Configure gives the same stuff as the basic box above, plus
two other features "Use system text" and "Display all headers".  Its buttons
are "Cancel" and "Set".

!Connect should use the same dialogue box as !Mail.
 

