----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Details:

MHill (26-Jan-98):

I tried to send an email with only the words "Large Attachment" in it and
attached an 839K text file to it.

The !Connect/!Mail refused to send it because it said the email was 1133K
and the maximum allowed was 1000K.

